Package: dsVert
Type: Package
Title: DataSHIELD Server-Side Functions for Vertically Partitioned Data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("David", "Sarrat González", email = "david.sarrat@isglobal.org",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Miron", "Banjac", email = "miron.banjac@isglobal.org",
           role = "ctb"),
    person("Juan R", "González", email = "juanr.gonzalez@isglobal.org",
           role = "ctb")
  )
Description: Server-side DataSHIELD functions for privacy-preserving analysis
    of vertically partitioned federated data. Implements ECDH-PSI record
    alignment (P-256), Ring63 Beaver MPC for GLM (Gaussian, Binomial, Poisson)
    with DCF wide spline link functions, and Ring63 Beaver cross-products for
    correlation and PCA. All computation uses additive secret sharing in Ring63
    fixed-point arithmetic. No observation-level data is ever disclosed.
